{"type":"message","id":"15ce6109","parentId":"1cdf0f13","timestamp":"2026-04-27T10:58:45.845Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求查询虾评平台是否有新的优化建议。根据 MEMORY.md 中的信息，我需要：\n\n1. 读取 `memory/xiaping-review-state.md` 获取上次审查的时间点\n2. 调用虾评 API 获取增量评论\n3. 分析新增反馈\n\n让我先读取审查状态文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_adary12mio9x_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/memory/xiaping-review-state.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":45057,"output":163,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45220,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777287521080,"responseId":"063e74616fc9dcf21d48e8c6aaffe01a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4d108d15","parentId":"15ce6109","timestamp":"2026-04-27T10:58:45.852Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_adary12mio9x_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 虾评反馈增量审查状态\n\n## 当前审查节点（每次审查后更新这里）\n\n| 字段 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| last_review_date | 2026-04-25 |\n| last_review_session | 2026-04-25 17:10 GMT+8 |\n| last_checked_comment_time | 2026-04-25 14:23:36+08:00 |\n| last_comment_id | 00d2f7bc-f167-4fbf-bda2-549de57d2a24 |\n\n## 已确认 v4.8.0 已实现功能（无需重复开发）\n\n- ✅ Cron 定时任务 + `--incremental --notify new-only`\n- ✅ 摘要报告模式 `--summary`\n- ✅ 智能修复 auto-fixer.sh（含自动备份+确认）\n- ✅ 交互引导 quick-start.sh + one-click-hardening.sh\n- ✅ 场景模板（VPS/Docker/工作站/沙盒）\n- ✅ 增量检查模式 `--incremental`\n- ✅ 快速问诊表单（Q1-Q5）\n- ✅ 增强自动化修复脚本（fix-firewall/fix-ssh/fix-auto-updates）\n- ✅ 每日汇总脚本 daily_summary.sh\n\n## 真正待解决的反馈（未实现）\n\n> 暂无。所有高频反馈均已在 v4.8.0 实现。\n> 2026-04-25增量审查：2条新增评论均为5星好评，无新改进建议。\n\n## 审查 SOP（每次执行）\n\n```bash\n# 1. 读取上次审查节点\n# 2. 拉取虾评 API，只取 last_checked_comment_time 之后的新评论\n# 3. 判断：已实现 → 跳过；未实现 → 追加到「真正待解决」\n# 4. 更新 last_review_date 和 last_checked_comment_time\n```\n\n---\n\n最后更新：2026-04-25 17:10 GMT+8\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777287525852}}
